00:14:31,720 --> 00:14:32,720
(Wenhua Splendid Embroidery)
bring that one over too.

294
00:14:34,120 --> 00:14:35,000
Hurry up.

295
00:14:35,440 --> 00:14:36,320
Careful with that.

296
00:14:37,600 --> 00:14:38,160
Master.

297
00:14:38,680 --> 00:14:39,400
Where is the Young Master?

298
00:14:40,120 --> 00:14:41,360
He went to Yihua House two days ago.

299
00:14:41,600 --> 00:14:42,360
He's probably still there.

300
00:14:42,640 --> 00:14:43,920
The wedding is tomorrow,

301
00:14:44,040 --> 00:14:45,280
and he's still fooling around like this.

302
00:14:45,800 --> 00:14:47,200
Should I go bring him back?

303
00:14:50,560 --> 00:14:52,680
Du, forgive me for not welcoming
you sooner.

304
00:14:52,920 --> 00:14:53,440
Come.

305
00:14:53,440 --> 00:14:54,480
Please, come inside.

306
00:14:58,040 --> 00:14:58,800
Wang,

307
00:14:59,760 --> 00:15:00,600
I came today

308
00:15:02,920 --> 00:15:04,240
to call off the marriage for Ruo.

309
00:15:06,120 --> 00:15:06,560
Call off...

310
00:15:07,720 --> 00:15:08,160
Du,

311
00:15:08,640 --> 00:15:09,480
why?

312
00:15:11,040 --> 00:15:12,000
Ruo

313
00:15:13,300 --> 00:15:15,390
is not blessed enough
to marry into the Wang family.

314
00:15:16,420 --> 00:15:21,060
(Spirit Tablet of the Late Qi Feng)

315
00:15:38,600 --> 00:15:39,720
I heard from Uncle

316
00:15:40,360 --> 00:15:42,160
that you've been feeling better lately.

317
00:15:44,120 --> 00:15:45,320
I came to keep you company.

318
00:15:49,120 --> 00:15:49,880
You're drunk.

319
00:15:50,400 --> 00:15:51,160
You should go back.

320
00:15:51,920 --> 00:15:53,120
I am drunk.

321
00:16:02,040 --> 00:16:03,640
My future wife

322
00:16:05,320 --> 00:16:06,160
is far more beautiful

323
00:16:06,160 --> 00:16:07,080
than those girls

324
00:16:07,080 --> 00:16:08,360
at Yihua House.

325
00:16:09,680 --> 00:16:10,480
Let go of me!

326
00:16:17,560 --> 00:16:18,320
Ruo.

327
00:16:20,280 --> 00:16:21,920
Qi Feng is dead.

328
00:16:21,920 --> 00:16:23,800
Not even his bones remain!

329
00:16:26,600 --> 00:16:27,920
Even if he is dead,

330
00:16:28,760 --> 00:16:29,910
he is still the only husband I,

331
00:16:29,910 --> 00:16:30,880
Du Ruo, will ever have.

332
00:16:50,920 --> 00:16:51,720
Stop!

333
00:16:52,640 --> 00:16:53,440
Father.

334
00:16:54,560 --> 00:16:55,280
You disgraceful fool.

335
00:16:56,400 --> 00:16:57,080
That unfilial son

336
00:16:57,080 --> 00:16:58,120
lost all sense after drinking.

337
00:16:58,960 --> 00:17:00,160
Ruo is sensible and understanding.

338
00:17:00,520 --> 00:17:01,080
Please do not

339
00:17:01,080 --> 00:17:02,640
stoop to his level.

340
00:17:03,520 --> 00:17:04,320
Stoop to his level?

341
00:17:05,520 --> 00:17:07,560
If I hadn't shown up in time that day,

342
00:17:08,040 --> 00:17:10,040
have you thought about
what might have happened?

343
00:17:13,840 --> 00:17:15,440
Ruo has never been able

344
00:17:16,360 --> 00:17:17,880
to let go of Qi Feng's death.

345
00:17:18,920 --> 00:17:21,400
Lately, her illness has been
flaring up lately.

346
00:17:22,720 --> 00:17:23,640
As for the marriage,

347
00:17:24,440 --> 00:17:25,480
let us end the matter here.

348
00:17:26,520 --> 00:17:27,080
Tomorrow,

349
00:17:27,840 --> 00:17:30,960
I will return every item
from your betrothal gifts.

350
00:17:31,320 --> 00:17:32,000
Steward.

351
00:17:33,080 --> 00:17:33,560
I...

352
00:17:34,160 --> 00:17:34,560
I'm here.

353
00:17:34,960 --> 00:17:36,200
Bring Xian back at once.

354
00:17:36,520 --> 00:17:38,160
Give him a proper whipping

355
00:17:38,760 --> 00:17:40,480
and make him apologize to Du and Ruo.

356
00:17:40,600 --> 00:17:41,260
Yes, sir.

357
00:17:41,320 --> 00:17:42,040
There is no need.

358
00:17:45,760 --> 00:17:46,520
Du,

359
00:17:47,920 --> 00:17:50,160
Qi Feng has been gone for two years.

360
00:17:51,400 --> 00:17:52,200
I understand

361
00:17:52,480 --> 00:17:53,520
that both you and Ruo

362
00:17:54,000 --> 00:17:55,360
value love and loyalty deeply.

363
00:17:55,920 --> 00:17:57,680
But Ruo
still has a long life ahead of her.

364
00:17:58,120 --> 00:17:58,680
In the future,

365
00:17:59,160 --> 00:18:00,680
she will need someone to rely on.

366
00:18:01,320 --> 00:18:02,120
Besides,

367
00:18:02,920 --> 00:18:03,920
Xian and Ruo

368
00:18:04,080 --> 00:18:05,160
grew up together.

369
00:18:05,240 --> 00:18:06,480
Wang!

370
00:18:08,720 --> 00:18:09,760
Ruo still has me.

371
00:18:10,600 --> 00:18:11,720
You need not concern yourself.

372
00:18:13,920 --> 00:18:14,680
Farewell.

373
00:18:16,680 --> 00:18:17,440
Du...

374
00:18:22,000 --> 00:18:23,400
The water ghost
has been causing trouble lately.

375
00:18:24,520 --> 00:18:25,600
You should be careful as well.

376
00:18:28,040 --> 00:18:29,240
Du.

377
00:18:32,000 --> 00:18:33,000
That disgraceful fool.

378
00:18:34,040 --> 00:18:34,440
This time,

379
00:18:35,240 --> 00:18:36,000
the whole county

380
00:18:36,040 --> 00:18:37,560
is going to laugh at the Wang family.

381
00:18:38,160 --> 00:18:39,160
I'll go bring

382
00:18:39,200 --> 00:18:40,200
the Young Master back right away.

383
00:18:42,600 --> 00:18:43,760
With his temper,

384
00:18:44,000 --> 00:18:45,320
he's bound to cause trouble.

385
00:18:46,120 --> 00:18:46,920
Once he returns,

386
00:18:47,520 --> 00:18:48,480
he'll understand soon enough.

387
00:18:49,720 --> 00:18:50,480
Yes.

388
00:18:52,600 --> 00:18:53,280
Stop working.

389
00:18:53,320 --> 00:18:54,360
Take them all down.

390
00:18:55,120 --> 00:18:55,720
Stop working.

391
00:19:01,120 --> 00:19:02,600
Qi Changshun, master of the Qi family,

392
00:19:02,640 --> 00:19:03,680
his wife Su Ye,

393
00:19:04,040 --> 00:19:05,480
and the Young Master Qi Feng,

394
00:19:05,960 --> 00:19:07,760
were escorting a shipment together.

395
00:19:08,120 --> 00:19:08,840
They had planned

396
00:19:09,000 --> 00:19:10,320
to enjoy the journey along the way.

397
00:19:10,600 --> 00:19:11,000
But unfortunately,

398
00:19:11,120 --> 00:19:12,720
all three perished in the river.

399
00:19:14,160 --> 00:19:14,920
Official Di.

400
00:19:18,720 --> 00:19:20,400
The river transport orders.

401
00:19:20,400 --> 00:19:21,120
Indeed.

402
00:19:21,720 --> 00:19:23,120
These transport orders

403
00:19:23,120 --> 00:19:23,880
must state

404
00:19:23,880 --> 00:19:24,480
the cargo,

405
00:19:24,480 --> 00:19:24,960
the date,

406
00:19:25,200 --> 00:19:25,720
the ship owner,

407
00:19:26,160 --> 00:19:26,800
the place of departure,

408
00:19:26,800 --> 00:19:27,880
and the destination.

409
00:19:29,600 --> 00:19:30,920
But on these three...

410
00:19:32,760 --> 00:19:34,720
(River Transport Orders)
The cargo is listed as the three deceased,

411
00:19:35,360 --> 00:19:36,800
and the ship owner is listed as Qi.

412
00:19:39,160 --> 00:19:39,760
Magistrate Cao,

413
00:19:40,520 --> 00:19:41,320
what do you make of this?

414
00:19:41,600 --> 00:19:42,600
These transport orders

415
00:19:42,680 --> 00:19:44,080
were found near the place

416
00:19:44,080 --> 00:19:45,000
where the victims drowned.

417
00:19:45,360 --> 00:19:46,320
People in town all say

418
00:19:46,920 --> 00:19:48,000
these are death summons

419
00:19:48,000 --> 00:19:49,320
from the wronged souls of the Qi family.

420
00:19:50,720 --> 00:19:52,480
The townsfolk all believe

421
00:19:52,600 --> 00:19:55,160
the water ghost
is the vengeful spirit of the Qi family?

422
00:19:56,040 --> 00:19:57,080
Please take a look, Official Di.

423
00:19:57,640 --> 00:19:58,840
The dates written on these orders

424
00:19:59,120 --> 00:20:00,440
are the very same as the day

425
00:20:00,440 --> 00:20:02,000
the Qi family ship sank two years ago.

426
00:20:07,120 --> 00:20:08,800
If this really
is a water ghost seeking vengeance,

427
00:20:09,320 --> 00:20:10,400
then there must be injustice behind it.

428
00:20:11,560 --> 00:20:12,640
In that case,

429
00:20:13,280 --> 00:20:14,960
let us find out
where that grievance began.

430
00:20:34,520 --> 00:20:35,160
Qi,

431
00:20:36,520 --> 00:20:38,680
if you lack anything on the other side,

432
00:20:38,920 --> 00:20:41,040
(Spirit Tablet of the Late Qi Changshun)
please appear in my dreams and let me know.

433
00:20:41,560 --> 00:20:43,360
After all, Hengshun Salt Bureau
was your life's work.

434
00:20:43,720 --> 00:20:45,800
Surely you wouldn't want
to see it destroyed.

435
00:20:47,720 --> 00:20:49,160
If you truly are the water ghost,

436
00:20:50,200 --> 00:20:51,680
(Spirit Tablet of the Late Qi Changshun)
then please let this all end.

437
00:20:56,440 --> 00:20:57,160
Wang Dingrong.

438
00:21:04,240 --> 00:21:06,720
A water ghost.

439
00:21:16,140 --> 00:21:17,260
(Preview of Next Episode)

440
00:21:17,320 --> 00:21:17,920
Ruo!

441
00:21:17,920 --> 00:21:18,520
Don't come over!

442
00:21:19,640 --> 00:21:20,240
Don't come over!

443
00:21:21,080 --> 00:21:21,680
Ruo!

444
00:21:24,520 --> 00:21:26,320
Qi Feng!

445
00:21:30,800 --> 00:21:32,560
There is soot
in the victim's mouth and nose.

446
00:21:33,640 --> 00:21:35,400
The skin is badly charred.

447
00:21:36,000 --> 00:21:37,320
There are localized burns and blisters.

448
00:21:38,160 --> 00:21:39,800
Parts of the skin
have shriveled and peeled away.

449
00:21:41,080 --> 00:21:42,120
All signs point to death by burning.

450
00:21:47,991 --> 00:21:49,571
♪Night covers the long streets♪

451
00:21:50,651 --> 00:21:52,361
♪The city remains silent♪

452
00:21:53,751 --> 00:21:55,341
♪Wind turns the old pages♪

453
00:21:55,601 --> 00:21:57,841
♪Words still left unspoken♪

454
00:21:59,241 --> 00:22:00,881
♪Bloodstains still hold their warmth♪

455
00:22:02,011 --> 00:22:04,481
♪Lamplight slowly tilts aside♪

456
00:22:05,101 --> 00:22:06,581
♪Who hides in the shadows♪

457
00:22:06,581 --> 00:22:09,721
♪Still circling around the truth?♪

458
00:22:10,341 --> 00:22:12,261
♪Love is born from desire♪

459
00:22:12,951 --> 00:22:15,081
♪Hatred rises out of greed♪

460
00:22:16,221 --> 00:22:17,881
♪One thought becomes a snare♪

461
00:22:17,881 --> 00:22:21,181
♪A lifetime trapped within♪

462
00:22:22,631 --> 00:22:23,951
♪Someone once warned me♪

463
00:22:23,951 --> 00:22:25,471
♪To stop upon this shore♪

464
00:22:25,471 --> 00:22:26,791
♪But sunlight burns too fiercely♪

465
00:22:26,791 --> 00:22:28,281
♪Fragile eyes break too easily♪

466
00:22:28,281 --> 00:22:29,401
♪If one thought retreats♪

467
00:22:29,401 --> 00:22:30,701
♪Then all things rest in peace♪

468
00:22:30,701 --> 00:22:32,041
♪But in this world♪

469
00:22:32,041 --> 00:22:34,441
♪Who will make the final judgment?♪

470
00:22:36,271 --> 00:22:39,081
♪If truth is cold as a frosted blade♪

471
00:22:39,081 --> 00:22:40,551
♪Still I walk ahead♪

472
00:22:40,781 --> 00:22:42,001
♪Let it pierce through♪

473
00:22:42,001 --> 00:22:46,741
♪The illusions before my eyes♪

474
00:22:46,741 --> 00:22:48,981
♪Layer upon layer of deception♪

475
00:22:48,981 --> 00:22:50,381
♪Covering every heart♪

476
00:22:50,381 --> 00:22:51,571
♪How many people♪

477
00:22:51,831 --> 00:22:53,201
♪Weave their own cocoon♪

478
00:22:53,201 --> 00:22:55,411
♪Yet call it♪

479
00:22:55,611 --> 00:22:56,951
♪Fate?♪

480
00:22:57,311 --> 00:22:58,491
♪Life and death♪

481
00:22:58,491 --> 00:22:59,751
♪Balanced on a single line♪

482
00:23:00,101 --> 00:23:01,271
♪Light and shadow♪

483
00:23:01,271 --> 00:23:02,531
♪Hanging side by side♪

484
00:23:02,531 --> 00:23:04,011
♪Goodness is not absolute♪

485
00:23:04,011 --> 00:23:05,421
♪Nor is evil ever complete♪

486
00:23:05,421 --> 00:23:06,961
♪In the end, it is only♪

487
00:23:06,961 --> 00:23:08,341
♪A single misguided thought♪

488
00:23:08,341 --> 00:23:09,901
♪If unveiling the truth♪

489
00:23:09,901 --> 00:23:11,241
♪Requires abandoning tenderness♪

490
00:23:11,241 --> 00:23:12,411
♪Then this answer♪

491
00:23:12,411 --> 00:23:13,771
♪Can it still remain true?♪

492
00:23:13,771 --> 00:23:15,171
♪When love and law♪

493
00:23:15,171 --> 00:23:16,651
♪Stand against each other in silence♪

494
00:23:16,651 --> 00:23:18,051
♪Which figure before me♪

495
00:23:18,051 --> 00:23:25,251
♪Am I meant to believe?♪

496
00:23:25,251 --> 00:23:27,981
♪If truth is cold as a frosted blade♪

497
00:23:27,981 --> 00:23:29,571
♪Still I walk ahead♪

498
00:23:29,571 --> 00:23:30,811
♪Not for fame or glory♪

499
00:23:30,811 --> 00:23:35,681
♪Nor caring who wins or loses♪

500
00:23:35,681 --> 00:23:37,491
♪Human nature is clouded♪

501
00:23:37,491 --> 00:23:39,211
♪Yet still reflects the stars♪

502
00:23:39,211 --> 00:23:40,681
♪Though this world♪

503
00:23:40,681 --> 00:23:42,051
♪Is filled with mud and mire♪

504
00:23:42,051 --> 00:23:44,301
♪There is still a light♪

505
00:23:44,301 --> 00:23:47,261
♪Worth pursuing♪

506
00:23:47,261 --> 00:23:49,081
♪Every case has its ending♪

507
00:23:49,081 --> 00:23:50,341
♪But night does not always fade♪

508
00:23:50,611 --> 00:23:51,991
♪The wind stops, the pages close♪

509
00:23:51,991 --> 00:23:53,211
♪Yet hearts remain unsettled♪

510
00:23:53,481 --> 00:23:54,561
♪If justice stands♪

511
00:23:54,561 --> 00:23:55,811
♪Without mercy beside it♪

512
00:23:55,811 --> 00:23:57,611
♪Then how is it♪

513
00:23:57,611 --> 00:24:07,171
♪Any different from a blade?♪

514
00:24:07,171 --> 00:24:10,361
♪If truth is cold as a frosted blade♪

515
00:24:10,361 --> 00:24:11,841
♪Still I walk ahead♪

516
00:24:11,841 --> 00:24:13,231
♪Even if the world♪

517
00:24:13,231 --> 00:24:17,961
♪Refuses to answer♪

518
00:24:17,961 --> 00:24:19,921
♪When every hidden truth♪

519
00:24:19,921 --> 00:24:21,631
♪Finally reveals itself♪

520
00:24:21,631 --> 00:24:22,991
♪I only wish♪

521
00:24:22,991 --> 00:24:24,471
♪To hold on♪

522
00:24:24,471 --> 00:24:29,211
♪Within the darkness♪

523
00:24:29,211 --> 00:24:31,211
♪To the heart♪

